Filter object in the following format:
`"filter" : {
"fieldName1": "value1",
"fieldName2":{"$operator":"value2"}
}`
Example of operators: `$eq`, `$ne`, `$lt`, `$lte`, `$gt`, `$gte`, `$in`, `$hasSome`, `$hasAll`, `$startsWith`, `$contains`.

